msgid ""
"Inventory Klein for Ray dependencies on Ray private APIs and Developer APIs."
msgstr "梳理 Klein for Ray 对 Ray 私有 API 和 Developer API 的依赖。"

msgid "Ray private-API inventory"
msgstr "Ray 私有 API 清单"

msgid ""
"The shipped `ray.klein` package has no direct imports from `ray._private`, "
"`ray.data._internal`, or `ray.air`. Bounded representations, batched column "
"validation and ragged arrays are implemented locally."
msgstr "发布的 `ray.klein` 包不直接从 `ray._private`、`ray.data._internal` 或 `ray.air` 导入。有限数据表示、分批列校验和不规则数组均在本地实现。"

msgid ""
"The project still uses several Ray Data extension classes whose stability is "
"DeveloperAPI rather than PublicAPI, including datasource and datasink base "
"classes. That is why the initial release intentionally supports only the Ray "
"2.56 minor line. Widening the range requires unit, integration, and clean-"
"wheel tests against the proposed Ray version."
msgstr "项目仍使用若干稳定性级别为 DeveloperAPI 而非 PublicAPI 的 Ray Data 扩展类，包括 datasource 和 datasink 基类。这正是首个版本有意仅支持 Ray 2.56 次版本系列的原因。扩展范围前，必须在拟支持的 Ray 版本上运行单元测试、集成测试和干净 wheel 测试。"

msgid ""
"CI rejects direct private imports. Code that requires a private Ray API is "
"not accepted into the package."
msgstr "CI 会拒绝直接导入私有 API。需要 Ray 私有 API 的代码不会被纳入该包。"
